{"id":544337,"link":"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/2016/11/报导者-香港不平静的释法夜晚/","date":"2016-11-09T02:25:51Z","modified":"2016-11-09T02:25:51Z","title":"报导者 | 香港不平静的释法夜晚","content":"<p>今年9月立法会选举，多名自决派和港独派的候选人透过一人一票的民主选举程序进入议会，成为数十万香港选民推举出来的代议士，走进建制内发声。两位“青年新政”的民选议员游蕙祯和梁颂恒，因宣誓典礼时作出不适当的行为，给予了中国政府一个整肃反对派的机会。中国政府跳过正当程序，直接进行释法，阻止青年新政的两名年青民选议员进入议会。战线就此一触即发。</p>\n<p><img class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-544338\" src=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/11/Screen-Shot-2016-11-08-at-下午6.22.34.png\" alt=\"screen-shot-2016-11-08-at-%e4%b8%8b%e5%8d%886-22-34\" width=\"585\" height=\"389\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/11/Screen-Shot-2016-11-08-at-下午6.22.34.png 585w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/11/Screen-Shot-2016-11-08-at-下午6.22.34-300x199.png 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 585px) 100vw, 585px\" /> <img class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-544339\" src=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/11/Screen-Shot-2016-11-08-at-下午6.22.27.png\" alt=\"screen-shot-2016-11-08-at-%e4%b8%8b%e5%8d%886-22-27\" width=\"584\" height=\"388\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/11/Screen-Shot-2016-11-08-at-下午6.22.27.png 584w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/11/Screen-Shot-2016-11-08-at-下午6.22.27-300x199.png 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 584px) 100vw, 584px\" /> <img class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-544340\" src=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/11/Screen-Shot-2016-11-08-at-下午6.22.17.png\" alt=\"screen-shot-2016-11-08-at-%e4%b8%8b%e5%8d%886-22-17\" width=\"585\" height=\"385\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/11/Screen-Shot-2016-11-08-at-下午6.22.17.png 585w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/11/Screen-Shot-2016-11-08-at-下午6.22.17-300x197.png 300w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/11/Screen-Shot-2016-11-08-at-下午6.22.17-230x150.png 230w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 585px) 100vw, 585px\" /> <img class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-544341\" src=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/11/Screen-Shot-2016-11-08-at-下午6.22.10.png\" alt=\"screen-shot-2016-11-08-at-%e4%b8%8b%e5%8d%886-22-10\" width=\"584\" height=\"390\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/11/Screen-Shot-2016-11-08-at-下午6.22.10.png 584w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/11/Screen-Shot-2016-11-08-at-下午6.22.10-300x200.png 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 584px) 100vw, 584px\" /> <img class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-544342\" src=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/11/Screen-Shot-2016-11-08-at-下午6.22.04.png\" alt=\"screen-shot-2016-11-08-at-%e4%b8%8b%e5%8d%886-22-04\" width=\"582\" height=\"387\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/11/Screen-Shot-2016-11-08-at-下午6.22.04.png 582w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/11/Screen-Shot-2016-11-08-at-下午6.22.04-300x199.png 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 582px) 100vw, 582px\" /> <img class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-544343\" src=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/11/Screen-Shot-2016-11-08-at-下午6.21.59.png\" alt=\"screen-shot-2016-11-08-at-%e4%b8%8b%e5%8d%886-21-59\" width=\"582\" height=\"385\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/11/Screen-Shot-2016-11-08-at-下午6.21.59.png 582w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/11/Screen-Shot-2016-11-08-at-下午6.21.59-300x198.png 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 582px) 100vw, 582px\" /> <img class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-544344\" src=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/11/Screen-Shot-2016-11-08-at-下午6.21.52.png\" alt=\"screen-shot-2016-11-08-at-%e4%b8%8b%e5%8d%886-21-52\" width=\"583\" height=\"386\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/11/Screen-Shot-2016-11-08-at-下午6.21.52.png 583w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/11/Screen-Shot-2016-11-08-at-下午6.21.52-300x199.png 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 583px) 100vw, 583px\" /> <img class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-544345\" src=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/11/Screen-Shot-2016-11-08-at-下午6.21.44.png\" alt=\"screen-shot-2016-11-08-at-%e4%b8%8b%e5%8d%886-21-44\" width=\"585\" height=\"390\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/11/Screen-Shot-2016-11-08-at-下午6.21.44.png 585w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/11/Screen-Shot-2016-11-08-at-下午6.21.44-300x200.png 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 585px) 100vw, 585px\" /></p>\n<p>示威者把铁马、竹枝、雨伞、垃圾桶筑成防线，只要可以阻挡警察前进的方法都用尽。“坚持死守”、“香港独立”，叫嚣声此起彼落，玻璃瓶碎裂声把示威者的愤怒放大，记者的闪光灯闪不停。那时候，大家都知道这个晚上一定很漫长，那时候才是9点半。随后双方持续对峙、谈判和割裂，冲突也愈演愈烈。直到深夜时分，真正的黑夜才来临。警方放弃防守的策略，改派机动性极高的“速龙小队”(即特别战术小队)，快速主动向示威者推进，他们戴上战术头盔和背心，手持盾牌和警棍，朝示威者方向推进和驱离。过程中，警方首次使用胡椒球发射枪，记者、示威者都被推倒在地上。到了深夜2点，警察的策略奏效，示威者亦散去。</p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n","author":996,"categories":[18271,18270,18269,18424],"tags":[31967,30435,8712,31966]}